import React from 'react';
import {  BrowserRouter  as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom';
import Header from './component/Header'
import About from './component/About'
import Culture from './component/Culture'
import Main from './component/Main'
import New from './component/news/New'
import {NewsContextProvider}  from './component/news/NewsContext'
import Footer from './component/Footer'
import Sales from './component/Sales'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap';
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';


function App() {
  return (
    <Router>

      <Route>
          <Header />

            <Switch>
                <Route path="/" exact component={Main} >
                          <NewsContextProvider>
                            <Main />
                            <New />
                          </NewsContextProvider>
                </Route>
              
              <Route path="/Culture.js"  exact component={Culture} />
             
              <Route path="/About.js"  exact component={About} />

              <Route path="/Sales.js"  exact component={Sales} />
          
            </Switch>
             

          <Footer />
      </Route>
            
      
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
